arts.ttl: Salah scores in Egypt World Cup qualifying win
arts.sum: Captain Mohamed Salah scored for Egypt as they eased to a 2-0 victory over Ethiopia in their 2026 World Cup qualifier on Friday, but 2022 semi-finalists Morocco needed a late winner from Bilal El Khannouss to defeat unfancied Niger.

arts.ttl: Mohamed Salah sent stark warning over two of his Liverpool team-mates
arts.sum: Mohamed Salah is enjoying his best-ever season in front of goal for Liverpool, but club legend John Barnes thinks Virgil van Dijk and Dominik Szoboszlai could pip him to prizes

arts.ttl: Nigeria get first qualifying win as Salah nets for Egypt
arts.sum: Victor Osimhen nets twice as Nigeria register their first victory in qualifying for the 2026 Fifa World Cup, while Algeria, Egypt and Ghana also win.

arts.ttl: Liverpool's current feelings on new Salah, Van Dijk contracts revealed
arts.sum: Seismic updates about the future of Liverpool's out-of-contract trio Mohamed Salah, Virgil van Dijk and Trent Alexander-Arnold suggest good news is on the way.

arts.ttl: Mo Salah Liverpool contract latest, Reds' 'poor' approach, Saudi shirt and Arne Slot view
arts.sum: Liverpool are set to lose Mohamed Salah on a free transfer this summer as things stand, with the Egyptian giving repeated hints that this will be his final season at Anfield following eight years
